# Build & Tooling

## Build System
- **Vite** for library build: `vite build --config vite.prod.config.ts`
- **vite-plugin-dts** generates `.d.ts` declaration files
- **vite-tsconfig-paths** resolves path aliases in Vite
- Output: `dist/` (ESM only, `dist/index.js` + `dist/index.d.ts`)

## TypeScript Checking
- Full check: `npm run check` (tsc --noEmit --skipLibCheck)
- Per-layer: `npm run check:core`, `check:runtime`, `check:storage`, `check:drivers`
- Each layer has its own `tsconfig.*.json` extending the base

## Path Aliases (tsconfig.json)
```
interaqt  → src/
@core     → src/core/index.ts
@runtime  → src/runtime/index.ts
@storage  → src/storage/index.ts
@drivers  → src/drivers/index.ts
```

## Release Process
- Uses `release-it` with `@release-it/conventional-changelog`
- Conventional Commits format for changelog generation
- Commit message: `chore(release): v${version}`
- Pre-release hook: runs `npm test && npm run build`
- Publishes to npm, pushes tags to git (branch: `main`)

## Testing
- Vitest: `npm test` (all), `npm run test:runtime`, `test:storage`, `test:core`
- Setup: `scripts/vitest.setup.js` polyfills `globalThis.crypto` for UUID generation
- Coverage: `@vitest/coverage-v8` available

## External Dependencies
DB drivers are dev dependencies only — consumers install their own:
`better-sqlite3`, `pg`, `mysql2`, `@electric-sql/pglite`
